{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "一個荒唐的早晨", "storyInfo": "邁克爾和瑪麗昂發生了衝突，另一邊，蒂比與莫伊拉則確認了她們的友誼。寧靜的夜晚過去，第二天早晨，場務霍汀在攝影棚發現了邁克爾和瑪麗昂被吊起的屍體。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，昨天晚上不是邁克爾第一次找你吧？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛來藍卡塢沒多久，以你的性格，如果不是對方死纏爛打，你一定不會去碰遠超自己職責範圍的事。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從道爾頓出了意外，組長被製片人辭退，我突然被要求接手道具組的第二天……邁克爾先生就找我了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想要在不經過正常程序、不驚動任何人的前提下離開這裡。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的意思是不告知格蕾塔女士，也不經過解約和地塊離境手續？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他是男主角，總會有人發現他離開的，到時候還是需要支付違約金啊？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非……他正在面臨某種更大的威脅，即使事後繳納違約金也要立刻離開這裡。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說道具組能接觸到所有工具，也很熟悉整個地塊的構造，如果是我……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該能想到辦法。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以你的能力，或許確實能想到辦法，但邁克爾的拍攝還沒有結束，如果他真的逃走了，你被發現了……格蕾塔女士不會放過你的。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，你有沒有想過，以後你就沒辦法在藍卡塢混下去了！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有想過，你的姐姐會有多傷心啊！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是說，你的家人都反對你來藍卡塢打拼，只有你的姐姐一直在鼓勵你？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你一定要做出成績來，不是為了要向家人證明什麼……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是希望不要讓姐姐失望，希望她能一直為我高興。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，你……你不要生氣好不好？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求你！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是氣你有事瞞著我。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你不會答應邁克爾，你只是不知道該怎麼拒絕他……我可以幫你的。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了，蒂比。我從來沒看過你這麼生氣……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看、看電影嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g12_dressingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你說，你想偷偷帶我走？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，親愛的。讓我們溫存一下，然後快點回房間拿行李，好嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕那個小道具師真的找到了辦法，能讓你避開地塊離境程序……但你能避開合約的違約條款嗎？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍攝還沒有結束，你知道格蕾塔那個女人的手段，她會讓你賠償天價的違約金！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都什麼時候了！還避開什麼合約，能避開那個殺人狂魔就行！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓死了，謝莉死了……你猜還有多久會輪到你和我？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，五年前那起意外發生的時候，你和我都曾對勞拉見死不救……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個殺人狂魔可能是勞拉的情人，可能是勞拉的老爸，或者某個自詡正義使者的怪俠……總之，他想害死那些與命案相關的人！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想讓我們懺悔，想讓我們贖罪！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，我要帶你離開這個是非之地，我們還要過漫長的餘生……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，真動聽。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，你什麼時候變得這麼深情了？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你對米蘭妮拋媚眼，和布景組的安娜、後勤組的米拉調情的時候……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，你的腦袋裡面想的竟然是和我度過漫長的餘生？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這是重點嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重點是——我不會走的，邁克爾。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你也不准走。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好不容易才為你爭取了在格蕾塔的劇組裡擔任主角的機會，一人分飾三角，多麼難得！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好把握，你將在藍卡塢一炮而紅！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們總會有別的機會……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著我，邁克爾。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在《杜邦夫人之死》裡的戲服甚至比米蘭妮——絕對女主角的戲服的做工更精緻更搶鏡……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你噴的香水、出席時裝週的服裝花的都是我的積蓄，甚至，這些讓你充當沃爾珀的假耳朵假尾巴也是我親手做的……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有我，觀眾們會發現你這個原本在鏡頭前光鮮亮麗的商品一下子就……沒有賣相了。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在一起五年了，我為你付出了一切。如今，我的積蓄不多了，年紀也不小了……我沒有時間再等了。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我愛你，邁克爾，別辜負我的愛。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣是——愛我？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓死的那天，你應該很感謝米蘭妮當眾點破了我們兩個的關係吧？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在所有人眼裡，我是個惹是生非的花花公子，而你付出了所有，卻連個名分都得不到，還要被別人嘲笑……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多可憐，多悲情！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不是嗎？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#4$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也說了，你只是在投資一件商品……投資，自然要捨得付出。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果道爾頓沒有變成一個爛酒鬼，你當初想辦法投資的應該就是他了吧？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就只是一條想要寄生卻找不到宿主的蟲子罷了，瑪麗昂。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓我覺得可笑……當然，我自己也可笑得不行。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話都說到了這個份上了，我一個人走，你就留在這裡吧。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你一個建議，你可以考慮投資那個叫盧西恩的小白臉，畢竟他第一次演電影就震驚了全劇組，很有投資潛力……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敢走出這裡，我馬上就去找格蕾塔檢舉你。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真是個冷血的瘋女人，你難道不怕那個殺人魔嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼要怕？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年，我是事後才知道勞拉為什麼會墜亡的。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見死不救的，只有你哦。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾，你在看什麼？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒像是狂潮，在瞬間將“沃爾珀”吞沒，他看向了化妝間角落的消防斧，握緊了拳頭。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——", "name": "蒂比&莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主角一行人不應該逃進動力層的！雖然地面上到處都是傀儡，但還是有辦法的……對吧，莫麗？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同意。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦進入移動城市的地下結構，空間一下子就變得很局限，所以被“邪靈”發現後，主角一行人根本無路可逃……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，他們被“邪靈”一個接著一個找出來，懸吊在通風管道上，在無邊的黑暗裡慢慢地等待死亡……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我參加過製作團隊的訪談活動，把人吊起來這段好像取材自哥倫比亞荒野上某些部落的儀式，懺悔啊審判啊之類的……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，雖然情節發展到這裡有點不符合邏輯，我還是很喜歡電影在動力層裡拍攝的這段。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼啊？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全都是實景拍攝哦！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據說是製作方已經沒錢再租地塊了，所以劇組偷偷潛入其他劇組的拍攝地塊，秘密拍完了這段……很刺激吧？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？等等……這部電影我之前也進電影院看過，為什麼好像沒看到過剛剛那幾個畫面？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，我們看的這張可是送審母帶的拷貝！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——這麼珍貴的東西，你是怎麼拿到的？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，身為一個資深的恐怖片愛好者，這是必備技能啦！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，你有秘密哦……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前就發現了，不管是電影本身，還是藍卡塢業內的各個方面，你懂得都比別人還多。一個布景噴畫師的見識有這麼廣嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，我生氣了！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我把壓箱底的寶貝拿出來跟你分享，希望你能開心一點，結果你卻開始審問我，嗚……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要哭不要哭，我不問了嘛。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們把注意力放在電影啦……莫麗，你不要老是分心！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被你發現了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，劇組最近發生的事情太多了，我……我有點緊張……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我在你身邊啊！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得也是！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你現在開心嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "duration": 60.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，你聽我說哦~", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管我是什麼身分，在這個劇組裡，我都是你最好最好的朋友！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕外面有殺人魔，身為好朋友，我也會保護你！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工作不順利，身為好朋友，我們要一起努力，噴畫師蒂比和道具師莫伊拉會成為藍卡塢的黃金恐怖片搭檔！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了，等到我們變成更好更好的朋友，我也會帶你去見我的家人……雖然不知道到時候對你來說會是驚喜還是驚嚇就是了！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那到時候，蒂比，我也要帶你去見我的姐姐！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以一起分享藍卡塢的故事，她會削蘋果給我們吃，她可以半分鐘削好一整個蘋果而且皮都不斷哦，你一定會喜歡她的！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這麼說定了！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老式電視機在熄燈的房間撐出一片光亮，也照亮兩個女孩的臉。各種離奇駭人的聲響迴盪著，但並不妨礙她們笑得燦爛。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們依偎在一起，用一種兩人熟悉的“恐慌”去抵禦恐慌，在一份生根發芽的友情之上去暢想未來。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個多麼難得的寧靜夜晚。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g1_setting_lobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$kjerag_n_intro", "key": "$kjerag_n_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的攝影棚怎麼這麼暗？", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#4$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，應該先問一下小莫伊拉的，她每天都很早來，最瞭解電源總開關在哪裡。", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#4$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道具間應該沒那麼遠啊，難道我一直在原地繞圈……嘶，有點不太對勁啊……", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？是我聽錯了吧？", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#3$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清晰的水滴聲在空寂的攝影棚裡迴盪，像在回應霍汀的疑問，但如此善解人意的“舉動”卻給她帶來更大的困惑和恐慌。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霍汀清楚地知道，自己所在的區域上方沒有水管，然而她聽到的聲音卻是從極近的地方傳來的。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰！到底是誰在那裡！", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們又想拿我找樂子，在收工之後把這個笑話當作下酒菜嗎？", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只、只要你們現在出來，我絕對不會怪你們！連小莫伊拉都參與了這個惡作劇？你們怎麼可以這樣教小孩子——", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#5$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-80", "duration": 0.6, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉喲——", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 60.0, "yTo": 0.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霍汀跌坐在地上，腰後傳來的異物感讓她意識到原來自己帶著手電筒。還沒等她自嘲，一股刺鼻的甜腥味撞進了她的鼻腔。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在驚恐中站起身，打開了手電筒——"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_creepy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_62_i03", "style": "cg", "pfrom": "0,-30", "pto": "0,0", "pduration": 10.0, "layer": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 3.0, "sfrom": 1.5, "sto": 1.0, "sduration": 60.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣風，懸吊在高處的繩索被吹動，那兩個霍汀再熟悉不過的人輕輕地晃動著，不爭不吵。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾與瑪麗昂，這對一直以來引發全劇組熱議的“戀人”，背對著迎接了死亡。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藉著微弱的光源，霍汀看清了他們的臉、他們的表情、他們身體擺動的幅度以及曼妙起舞的灰塵……"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她感受到了一種，難以言喻的詭異和……神聖。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然想起，蒂比之前拉著自己看恐怖片的時候說過……"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哥倫比亞荒原上某些部落的儀式裡，懸吊代表著對死者的審判，代表著對有罪生者的警示。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到烈日的曝曬使得屍體開裂，直到所有人都認為他們罪有應得，直到繩子再也承受不了罪惡的重量——"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "channel": "a", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "砰！"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快、快來人啊——！", "name": "倒楣的場務"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒楣的場務踉蹌著向外面跑去，她想——"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個多麼荒唐的早晨。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}